        "## 2.7 Dictionary\n",
        "\n",
        "**Dictionary** adalah koleksi data dengan **pasangan key-value** (kunci-nilai). Kita menggunakan **kurung kurawal** `{}` untuk membuat dictionary.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Kapan gunakan dictionary?** Ketika punya data yang punya banyak atribut (contoh: data mahasiswa punya NIM, nama, kelas, angkatan)."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# Buat dictionary untuk 1 mahasiswa\n",
        "mhs_budi = {\n",
        "    \"nim\": \"1301213001\",\n",
        "    \"nama\": \"Budi Santoso\",\n",
        "    \"kelas\": \"IF-A\",\n",
        "    \"angkatan\": 2023,\n",
        "    \"ipk\": 3.75\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Dictionary mahasiswa:\", mhs_budi)\n",
        "print(f\"\\nNIM: {mhs_budi['nim']}\")\n",
        "print(f\"Nama: {mhs_budi['nama']}\")\n",
        "print(f\"IPK: {mhs_budi['ipk']}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# Tambah key baru ke dictionary\n",
        "mhs_budi = {\"nim\": \"1301213001\", \"nama\": \"Budi Santoso\", \"kelas\": \"IF-A\"}\n",
        "print(\"Awal:\", mhs_budi)\n",
        "\n",
        "mhs_budi[\"angkatan\"] = 2023  # Tambah key baru\n",
        "mhs_budi[\"ipk\"] = 3.75\n",
        "print(\"Setelah tambah key:\", mhs_budi)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Update value\n",
        "mhs_budi[\"ipk\"] = 3.80  # Ubah value IPK\n",
        "print(\"Setelah update IPK:\", mhs_budi)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Method: keys(), values(), items()\n",
        "print(f\"\\nKunci (keys): {list(mhs_budi.keys())}\")\n",
        "print(f\"Nilai (values): {list(mhs_budi.values())}\")\n",
        "print(f\"Pasangan (items): {list(mhs_budi.items())}\")"
      ]
    },
