        "# BAGIAN 3: Control Flow — Membuat Keputusan & Perulangan"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 3.1 If-Elif-Else\n",
        "\n",
        "**If-Elif-Else** digunakan untuk membuat keputusan berdasarkan kondisi.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Logika:**\n",
        "- `if kondisi:` — JIKA kondisi benar, lakukan kode ini\n",
        "- `elif kondisi lain:` — JIKA TIDAK, TETAPI kondisi lain benar, lakukan ini\n",
        "- `else:` — JIKA TIDAK ADA kondisi yang benar, lakukan ini"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# Contoh 1: Cek status mahasiswa berdasarkan angkatan\n",
        "angkatan_mahasiswa = 2023\n",
        "tahun_sekarang = 2024\n",
        "tahun_masuk = angkatan_mahasiswa\n",
        "tahun_lulus = tahun_masuk + 4  # Asumsikan studi 4 tahun\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"Tahun masuk: {tahun_masuk}\")\n",
        "print(f\"Tahun lulus: {tahun_lulus}\")\n",
        "print(f\"Tahun sekarang: {tahun_sekarang}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "if tahun_sekarang < tahun_masuk:\n",
        "    status = \"Belum masuk\"\n",
        "elif tahun_sekarang < tahun_lulus:\n",
        "    status = \"Aktif\"\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    status = \"Lulus\"\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"\\nStatus mahasiswa angkatan {angkatan_mahasiswa}: {status}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# Contoh 2: Labelisasi beban SKS (ringan, normal, berat)\n",
        "total_sks = 15\n",
        "\n",
        "if total_sks < 12:\n",
        "    label_beban = \"Ringan\"\n",
        "elif total_sks <= 20:\n",
        "    label_beban = \"Normal\"\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    label_beban = \"Berat\"\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"Total SKS: {total_sks} → Beban: {label_beban}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# Test dengan SKS berbeda\n",
        "for sks in [8, 15, 24]:\n",
        "    if sks < 12:\n",
        "        label = \"Ringan\"\n",
        "    elif sks <= 20:\n",
        "        label = \"Normal\"\n",
        "    else:\n",
        "        label = \"Berat\"\n",
        "    print(f\"SKS {sks} → {label}\")"
