        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# BAGIAN 4: Error Handling — Mengatasi Error dengan Elegan"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 4.1 Apa itu Error?\n",
        "\n",
        "**Error** adalah situasi di mana kode tidak bisa dijalankan karena ada masalah. Error umum yang akan kita temui:\n",
        "\n",
        "| Error | Penyebab | Contoh |\n",
        "|-------|----------|--------|\n",
        "| **NameError** | Variabel tidak didefinisikan | `print(nama)` (nama belum ada) |\n",
        "| **TypeError** | Tipe data salah | `\"10\" + 5` (string + integer) |\n",
        "| **KeyError** | Key dictionary tidak ada | `data['kunci_salah']` |\n",
        "| **ValueError** | Konversi tipe gagal | `int(\"abc\")` |\n",
        "| **IndexError** | Index list out of range | `list[99]` (index tidak ada) |\n",
        "| **ZeroDivisionError** | Bagi dengan nol | `10 / 0` |\n",
        "\n",
        "Dengan **error handling**, kita bisa menangkap error dan memberi pesan yang lebih user-friendly."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code">
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# Mari kita lihat contoh error yang akan terjadi\n",
        "# Uncomment baris di bawah untuk lihat error:\n",
        "\n",
        "# ValueError: konversi string \"tiga\" ke integer gagal\n",
        "# value = int(\"tiga\")  # Error!\n",
        "\n",
        "# ZeroDivisionError: bagi dengan 0\n",
        "# result = 10 / 0  # Error!\n",
        "\n",
        "# TypeError: operasi string + integer\n",
        "# text = \"Nilai: \" + 42  # Error!\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Error di atas akan terjadi kalau dijalankan. Kita akan tangani dengan try-except!\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 4.2 Try-Except\n",
        "\n",
        "**Try-Except** adalah pola untuk menangkap error tanpa program crash.\n",
        "\n",
        "```python\n",
        "try:\n",
        "    # Kode yang mungkin error\n",
        "except ErrorType:\n",
        "    # Apa yang lakukan kalau error terjadi\n",
        "```"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code">
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# Contoh 1: Tangkap ValueError\n",
        "sks_text = \"tiga\"  # Data kotor: string bukan angka\n",
        "\n",
        "try:\n",
        "    sks = int(sks_text)  # Coba konversi\n",
        "    print(f\"SKS: {sks}\")\n",
        "except ValueError:\n",
        "    print(f\"❌ Error: '{sks_text}' bukan angka! Gunakan nilai numerik.\")\n",
        "    sks = None  # Set default value\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"SKS yang diproses: {sks}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code">
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# Contoh 2: Tangkap KeyError\n",
        "mhs_data = {\"nim\": \"1301213001\", \"nama\": \"Budi Santoso\", \"kelas\": \"IF-A\"}\n",
        "\n",
        "try:\n",
        "    ipk = mhs_data[\"ipk\"]  # Key 'ipk' tidak ada\n",
        "except KeyError as error:\n",
        "    print(f\"⚠️ Warning: Key {error} tidak ada di data mahasiswa\")\n",
        "    print(f\"Data yang ada: {list(mhs_data.keys())}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code">
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# Contoh 3: Tangkap ZeroDivisionError\n",
        "def hitung_rata_rata(nilai_list):\n",
        "    \"\"\"Hitung rata-rata dengan error handling\"\"\"\n",
        "    try:\n",
        "        total = sum(nilai_list)\n",
        "        jumlah = len(nilai_list)\n",
        "        rata_rata = total / jumlah\n",
        "        return rata_rata\n",
        "    except ZeroDivisionError:\n",
        "        print(\"❌ Error: List kosong! Tidak bisa hitung rata-rata.\")\n",
        "        return None\n",
        "\n",
        "# Test dengan list normal\n",
        "nilai_1 = [85, 90, 78]\n",
        "rata_1 = hitung_rata_rata(nilai_1)\n",
        "print(f\"Rata-rata [85, 90, 78]: {rata_1:.2f}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# Test dengan list kosong\n",
        "nilai_2 = []\n",
        "rata_2 = hitung_rata_rata(nilai_2)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 4.3 Try-Except-Else-Finally\n",
        "\n",
        "Pola lengkap untuk error handling:\n",
        "- `try:` — kode yang mungkin error\n",
        "- `except:` — apa yang lakukan kalau error\n",
        "- `else:` — apa yang lakukan kalau TIDAK ada error (opsional)\n",
        "- `finally:` — selalu jalankan, terlepas error atau tidak (opsional)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code">
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# Contoh: Baca dan proses data dari list\n",
        "data_list = [{\"nama\": \"Budi\", \"nilai\": \"85\"}, {\"nama\": \"Ani\", \"nilai\": \"abc\"}, {\"nama\": \"Citra\", \"nilai\": \"90\"}]\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Memproses data mahasiswa:\\n\")\n",
        "berhasil = 0\n",
        "gagal = 0\n",
        "\n",
        "for data in data_list:\n",
        "    try:\n",
        "        nama = data[\"nama\"]\n",
        "        nilai = int(data[\"nilai\"])  # Coba konversi ke integer\n",
        "    except ValueError:\n",
        "        print(f\"❌ {data['nama']}: Nilai '{data['nilai']}' bukan angka. Lewati.\")\n",
        "        gagal += 1\n",
        "    except KeyError as error:\n",
        "        print(f\"❌ Key {error} tidak ada. Lewati.\")\n",
        "        gagal += 1\n",
        "    else:\n",
        "        # Jalankan HANYA kalau tidak ada error\n",
        "        print(f\"✅ {nama}: Nilai {nilai} (valid)\")\n",
        "        berhasil += 1\n",
        "    finally:\n",
        "        # Jalankan selalu (untuk logging, cleanup, dll)\n",
        "        pass\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"\\nRingkasan: {berhasil} berhasil, {gagal} gagal\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 4.4 Validasi Data\n",
        "\n",
        "Buatlah fungsi untuk validasi data sebelum diproses lebih lanjut."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code">
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# Fungsi validasi: cek apakah data mahasiswa lengkap\n",
        "def validasi_mahasiswa(mhs_data):\n",
        "    \"\"\"Validasi data mahasiswa. Return True jika valid, False jika tidak.\"\"\"\n",
        "    # Cek apakah ada field yang required\n",
        "    required_fields = [\"mahasiswa_id\", \"nim\", \"nama_lengkap\", \"kelas\", \"angkatan\"]\n",
        "    \n",
        "    for field in required_fields:\n",
        "        if field not in mhs_data:\n",
        "            print(f\"❌ Field '{field}' tidak ada\")\n",
        "            return False\n",
        "        \n",
        "        value = mhs_data[field]\n",
        "        \n",
        "        # Cek apakah value kosong/null\n",
        "        if value is None or value == \"\":\n",
        "            print(f\"⚠️  Field '{field}' kosong\")\n",
        "            return False\n",
        "    \n",
        "    # Cek tipe data\n",
        "    if not isinstance(mhs_data[\"mahasiswa_id\"], int):\n",
        "        print(f\"❌ 'mahasiswa_id' harus integer, bukan {type(mhs_data['mahasiswa_id']).__name__}\")\n",
        "        return False\n",
        "    \n",
        "    if not isinstance(mhs_data[\"angkatan\"], int):\n",
        "        print(f\"❌ 'angkatan' harus integer, bukan {type(mhs_data['angkatan']).__name__}\")\n",
        "        return False\n",
        "    \n",
        "    return True\n",
        "\n",
        "# Test validasi\n",
        "print(\"Data 1 (Valid):\")\n",
        "data1 = {\"mahasiswa_id\": 1, \"nim\": \"1301213001\", \"nama_lengkap\": \"Budi Santoso\", \"kelas\": \"IF-A\", \"angkatan\": 2023}\n",
        "is_valid = validasi_mahasiswa(data1)\n",
        "print(f\"Valid: {is_valid}\\n\")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Data 2 (Nama kosong):\")\n",
        "data2 = {\"mahasiswa_id\": 2, \"nim\": \"1301213002\", \"nama_lengkap\": \"\", \"kelas\": \"IF-A\", \"angkatan\": 2023}\n",
        "is_valid = validasi_mahasiswa(data2)\n",
        "print(f\"Valid: {is_valid}\\n\")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Data 3 (Angkatan string):\")\n",
        "data3 = {\"mahasiswa_id\": 3, \"nim\": \"1301213003\", \"nama_lengkap\": \"Citra Dewi\", \"kelas\": \"IF-B\", \"angkatan\": \"2023\"}\n",
        "is_valid = validasi_mahasiswa(data3)\n",
        "print(f\"Valid: {is_valid}\")"
      ]
    },
